article.description: — Lucas Williamson posted 18 points and six rebounds as Loyola of Chicago routed Illinois State 90-60 on Sunday in the Missouri Valley Conference opener for both teams.
article.headline: Williamson leads Loyola of Chicago over Illinois St. 90-60
article.linkText: Williamson leads Loyola of Chicago over Illinois St. 90-60
article.story: CHICAGO -- — Lucas Williamson posted 18 points and six rebounds as Loyola of Chicago routed Illinois State 90-60 on Sunday in the Missouri Valley Conference opener for both teams. Cameron Krutwig added 15 points (5-2), and Tom Welch chipped in 10 points. DJ Horne had 18 points for the Redbirds (3-4). Dedric Boyd added 17 points. Dusan Mahorcic had eight rebounds. The teams meet again on Monday. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
